law.history: Repealed 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 117, sec. 3, effective July 15, 1998; and ch. 226, sec. 113, effective July 15, 1998. -- Amended 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 178, sec. 2, effective July 15, 1982. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 114, sec. 23. -- Created 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 59, sec. 1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Authority to execute Interstate Emergency Management and Disaster Compact.
metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/98). This section was repealed by 1998 Ky. Acts. chs. 117 and 226.
